{
  "stem": "8786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was in a high position and he gave me a pair of army shoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But it wasn't a pair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the left was one-- the left one was a little bit smaller.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this is a good thing to learn, a lesson.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "If your shoes are tight, it's very easy to freeze, because there's no air to keep it warm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And up to the present day, I'm suffering from three toes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I had cellulitis about 25 times because of these frozen toes-- my left-- on my left foot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They're twice the size of the normal-- of the other ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And because of these frozen toes, I was given a vacation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I didn't have to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from every-- every-- every bad part has some positive in it too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And what I was doing was a dangerous thing, but I did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I had a ticket to stay home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And middle of the day, I was hiding two of my friends under my blanket, because it was cold.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "In daytime, you stay inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You're not supposed to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And then, those young kids came with their gun to see that I have a paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I have two boys hiding under my blanket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "If they would-- if they would just go like this, we would all be killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 'til a few weeks before Passover this was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden my doctor-- the same doctor who was-- who took care of my frozen toe, he says, you know what?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think you should leave that place already, because this place was full of people who were sick with typhus.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're much better off to go out from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told him, but I have my friends there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
